# Sverklo Full Demo — for DevHunt / Product Hunt
Output docs/demo-full.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 900
Set Height 520
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Shell "zsh"

Hide
Type "cd ~/projects/research/product/sverklo"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "# 1. Health audit — grade your codebase in seconds"
Enter
Sleep 600ms

Type "sverklo audit | head -20"
Enter
Sleep 10s

Type ""
Enter
Sleep 400ms

Type "# 2. Publish a dynamic badge for your README"
Enter
Sleep 600ms

Type "sverklo audit --badge"
Enter
Sleep 10s

Type ""
Enter
Sleep 400ms

Type "# 3. Works with Claude Code, Cursor, Windsurf, Zed"
Enter
Sleep 400ms

Type "# Install: npm install -g sverklo && sverklo init"
Enter
Sleep 2s
